    "attributes": {
        "action": "Raise the Universal Credit allowance for over 18s to match people aged 25 & over",
        "additional_details": "When people turn 18 they are adults and they often move out of their parents\u2019 house and with that lower rate they can't support themselves, so I request the government to raise universal credit for all over 18s to the same as over 25s.",
        "background": "Raise the standard universal credit allowance from \u00a3342.72 to \u00a3409.89 for everyone (not in a couple) over 18.",
